{"tid":1829791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平誤譯為「Mr Shithole」　Facebook 致歉","createTime":"2020-01-19T05:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T05:41:06.000Z","uid":23064,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f678571675faeedd9f2e4456687e1a1953c6bc16","tid":1829791,"uid":23064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:32:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42aW1qf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42aW1qf.png&h=69635061&s={SIZE}\" /></div> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">背景圖片：CGTN報道影片截圖</div></span><br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平結束緬甸國事訪問啟程回國，他與國務資政昂山素姬舉行會談後，發表聯合聲明，高度評價中緬關係。不過，訪緬之旅卻發生一段插曲，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">昂山素姬在其官方Facebook 網頁，以緬甸文發表有關今次訪問的貼文，內容自動翻譯成英文後，習近平被譯成「Mr Shithole」（糞坑先生）</span></strong>，Facebook就事件致歉，強調是技術問題。<br />\n<br />\n習近平這次出訪緬甸是中國領導人近20年來的首次對緬訪問，惟緬甸 facebook 頁面自動翻譯功能出現錯誤，將習近平的姓名從緬甸文翻成英文時誤翻成「Mr Shithole」（糞坑先生）。昂山素姬的Facebook帖文，被翻譯成「Mr Shithole, President of China arrives at 4 PM」（中國國家主席糞坑先生於下午4時抵達），「President of China, Mr. Shithole, signed a guest record of the house of representatives」（中國國家主席糞坑先生在下院人民院貴賓簿上簽名）。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 發言人稱，已修復了一項技術問題，有關問題導致 facebook 從緬甸文翻成英文時發生翻譯錯誤，facebook 強調正採取措施，以確保之後不再發生，「我們誠摯地對冒犯表示歉意。」Facebook 解釋，在緬甸文的翻譯資料庫中並沒有習近平的姓名。在這種情況下，臉書的系統會猜測字詞，並用相似音節的字詞來替換。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 又稱，已在 facebook 上用緬甸文其他與「習近平」相似的字詞進行測試，而臉書發現，在緬甸文中其他以 xi 和 shi 音節開頭的字詞，同樣被翻譯成「Shithole」。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook過去將緬甸文翻譯成英文時，亦發生過類復問題，2018年在翻譯一則反羅興亞、支持殺害穆斯林的Facebook貼文時，帖文被譯成「我在緬甸不應該有彩虹（I shouldn't have a rainbow in Myanmar）。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：路透社<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Source: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/習近平誤譯為-mr-shithole-facebook-致歉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%AA%A4%E8%AD%AF%E7%82%BA-mr-shithole-facebook-%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1Kix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=a6f2d982\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%AA%A4%E8%AD%AF%E7%82%BA-mr-shithole-facebook-%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89&h=1fb9a9b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/習近平誤譯為-mr-shithole-facebook-致歉</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e42bf56576ef32446336b682f767354b33adcbf","tid":1829791,"uid":263944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"fb 前線係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9eae79b41a369c287a45d8d88a6c89af3316ce","tid":1829791,"uid":316700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"根本都冇譯錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過昴山素姫好地地奶共我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63f0defd9c67458fbde5cbef03891784bdc130c","tid":1829791,"uid":140218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定嚇到Suckerberg屎眼都縮"},{"pid":"646239b648b3fa1883a76c635f0538e181cfc9de","tid":1829791,"uid":54502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"Mr Shithole<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小學生又多個花名"},{"pid":"631df31512f9a48f114217ca1fd379dd3bc9afd2","tid":1829791,"uid":56261,"like":